# Workspace agent instructions

Copy to `Agent.md` (or `AGENTS.md`) in your project root.
Loaded every task run into the system prompt (**default max 8000 chars**).

**Framework-bound conventions are built-in** (skills / memory paths / plan+specs
artifacts / default work style / b64 tool tips). Do **not** re-copy those here —
keep this file for **project-only** rules so you use the budget for custom content.

